title: .NET Conf 2023 - Watch party @ SSW
eventDescription:
​Attention .NET enthusiasts! 🎓

SSW invites you to our .NET Conf day on November 14th. Get into the most popular topics this year straight from Microsoft Stack experts, covering AI, web development, mobile development, game development, and more. We will have presentations playing live all day, and snacks and conversations to go around. If you code in C# or are interested in .NET, this is the place to be!

More about .NET Conf

Highlight ⭐: Our own Luke Parker's presentation was selected by Microsoft and will be playing - "Vertical Slice Architecture: How Does it Compare to Clean Architecture?"

Agenda
Details to be confirmed. Stay tuned!

Offices
SSW Sydney – Watch party 🎦
SSW Melbourne – Watch party 🎦
SSW Brisbane – Watch party 🎦
SSW Newcastle – Watch party 🎦

Don't miss this chance to deepen your dev skills and network with other .NET professionals. Register your attendance now!
P.S. Share this event with anyone who might find it valuable. The more, the merrier!
